 compact cameras for the perfect shot every time</span></a></h2></div></div><div class="sc-qm89yg-0 kwwnpV sc-qm89yg-1 bXiCyl hero-article article-best article-image-overlay"><div class="sc-ntudqq-0 ifksOd image-wrap"><a href="/extras/indybest/gadgets-tech/cameras-accessories/best-action-cameras-b2123974.html" aria-label="Read more about action cameras indybest" class="sc-ntudqq-1 hAUzrd"><img src="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/07/13/12/action%20cameras%20indybest%20copy.jpg?quality=75&width=640&crop=3%3A2%2Csmart&auto=webp" srcSet="https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/07/13/12/action%20cameras%20indybest%20copy.jpg?quality=75&width=375&auto=webp 375w, https://static.independent.co.uk/2022/07/13/12/action%20cameras%20indybest%20copy.jpg?quality=75&width=640&auto=webp 640w" loading="lazy" alt="<p>Watch out for the levels of stabilisation if you’re set on taking them out into the wild  </p>" class="sc-1mc30lb-0 dIbDxL sc-ntudqq-2 egJWsc"></a></div><div class="sc-1p30kpk-1 glXtbw capsules"><a href="/extras/indybest/gadgets-tech/cameras-accessories" class="sc-1p30kpk-0 hYvwLR capsule">Cameras & Accessories</a></div><div class="content"><h2 class="sc-9tb5ao-0 bXiXts"><a class="title" href="/extras/indybest/gadgets-tech/cameras-accessories/best-action-cameras-b2123974.html"><span class="highlight">9 best</span><span> action cameras that will ensure you never miss a shot</span></a></h2></div></div><div class="sc-qm89yg-0 kwwnpV sc-qm89yg-1 bXiCyl hero-article article-best article-image-overlay"><div class="sc-ntudqq-0 ifksOd image-wrap"><a href="/extras/indybest/gadgets-tech/cameras-accessories/best-vlogging-camera-b1841740.html" aria-label="Read more about Vlogging cameras.jpg" class="sc-ntudqq-1 hAUzrd"><img src="https://static.independent.co.uk/2021/05/05/11/Vlogging%20cameras.jpg?quality=75&width=640&crop=3%3A2%2Csmart&auto=webp" srcSet="https://static.independent.co.uk/2021/05/05/11/Vlogging%20cameras.jpg?quality=75&width=375&auto=webp 375w, https://static.in